snippet.title: Rainstorm EP Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Rainstorm EP is a wistful poem to found lost things and rainy nights, the love child of a music box and a snowglobe.
Game by Jakey Mumfie and Jake Grizzly Pierce.

Buy now! (itch.io): https://jakegrizzlypierce.itch.io/rainstorm-ep
About Ice Water Games: https://linktr.ee/icewatergames

Trailer by Brendan Cook.
•  website (http://brendancook.xyz/)  
•  instagram (https://www.instagram.com/vidgoblin/)  
•  vimeo (https://vimeo.com/brendancook)
